svg.title: Finnest
svg.desc: Thousands of private investors from Germany, Austria, Switzerland and Slovakia have already registered with Finnest. At Finnest you can do what professional investors have been doing for decades: invest seriously in established medium-sized companies. Simple and with maximum interest. Private investors appreciate our platform, that they can invest in successful companies with history. They prefer to invest their money cautiously and in the traditional values of domestic companies with good credit ratings.
